The paper focuses on object detection systems using deep neural networks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the testing and evaluation of these systems, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and software engineering (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper addresses the potential for errors in these systems, which could fall under computer security and cryptography (cs.CR).
